vote.title: Authorize an amendment to the FY 2022-23 Cultural Organization Program Guidelines, previously authorized on January 26, 2022, by Resolution No. 22-0239, to expand eligibility criteria for returning applicants related to COVID-19 and organization transition - Financing: This action has no cost consideration (see Fiscal Information)
